# Local-only — do not push to public repo.
# Only on-chain referenced pack files are tracked.
# Filenames kept short (rNNN.json) to give breathing room in the
# 128-byte commitment limit (64 hash + 1 pipe + URL ≤ 128).
# - pack.json     → historical r42 (UID 226 — superseded)
# - pack_r87.json → historical r87 (UID 21  — superseded)
# - r102.json     → historical r102 "Output First" (UID 226 — superseded by r104)
# - r103.json     → historical r103 "Authorized Audit" (UID 21 — superseded by r106 then r108)
# - r104.json     → historical r104 (UID 226 — chain score 1.32 ep 1234, superseded by r109)
# - r106.json     → historical r106 (UID 21 — pre-eval FAIL on §11 cribsheet, superseded by r108)
# - r108.json     → historical r108 (UID 21 — chain score 1.76 ep 1242, superseded by r111)
# - r109.json     → UID 226 (gor-hotkey-01) — r109 (= r108 content, awaiting cross-UID challenge)
# - r111.json     → UID 21  (gor-hotkey-02) — r111 "Engineering Operating Protocol" (formal scenario-aware standards, modeled on UID 56/58 passing packs)
*
!.gitignore
!pack.json
!pack_r87.json
!r102.json
!r103.json
!r104.json
!r106.json
!r108.json
!r109.json
!r111.json
